# Purchases Decomposition (Power BI report)

The _Purchases Decomposition_ report breaks down the total amount of all purchasing activities by item categories, vendors, fiscal periods, and document types. It helps with understanding the purchasing costs and analysing the spending patterns within the organization.

This report is designed for finance and purchasing teams.

